                TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts4">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>haḏōl al yāklūn ᵊḥqūq al-ʕibād, daḥḥiǧ yā xayyo! </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
